+++ ##b00|The International Translation Archive needs YOU to join the Review Team!##

You are fluent in English? You want to help the Archive out? Apply today for the Review Team.

Your duties would be to review our translations for:
* scientifical tone
* expression
* spelling and grammar
As a member of the Review Team you would be a staff member, and gain access to our illustrious staff site and the Review Team's chat.

Who can apply? Everyone fluent in English, native speaker or not. Also already being staff in the archive or another wiki has no influence on membership in the Review Team.

How to apply? Just answer to [http://scp-int.wikidot.com/forum/t-2150084/the-review-team-recruitment-thread this thread] or send a PM to [[*user LadyKatie]] here or on our Discord. You will be asked to correct a short article or section of an article to test your skills then.

-- //The Archive's staff//


PS. You don't want to join the Review Team but to help checking translations? Just see the box below for articles in need.

